ass=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Subcon Work Order &amp; RA Billing</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"ocsp3-group-row\"><td class=\"ocsp3-td\" colspan=\"4\">Finance &amp; Controls</td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Payments &amp; Expenses</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">RFQ &amp; Purchase Orders</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Staff Payroll</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Multi-Level Approvals</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">RA Bills &amp; Client Invoicing</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"ocsp3-group-row\"><td class=\"ocsp3-td\" colspan=\"4\">Enterprise</td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Custom Roles</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Vendor &amp; Client Portal</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">White-Label Solution</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Zoho / Tally / SAP Integration</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"ocsp3-td\">Unlimited Users</td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-dash\">—</span></td><td class=\"ocsp3-td\"><span class=\"ocsp3-tick\">✓</span></td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ocsp4-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-wrap\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-head ocsp4-anim\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-eyebrow\"><span class=\"ocsp4-ey-dot\"></span>Why SiteFlow</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-h2\">Everything you need to run <em class=\"ocsp4-h2-em\">projects profitably.</em></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-grid\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-card ocsp4-anim ocsp4-d1\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-bar\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp4-icon\">🕐</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-title\">24×7 Support</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp4-body\">Round-the-clock support from a team that understands real construction workflows — WhatsApp, Google Meet, or phone. Built for teams across shifts and time zones.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-card ocsp4-anim ocsp4-d2\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-bar\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp4-icon\">🚀</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-title\">Fast Onboarding</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp4-body\">Complete onboarding, data setup, and hands-on training so your team goes live confidently from day one. No long learning curves, no heavy IT support needed.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-card ocsp4-anim ocsp4-d3\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-bar\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp4-icon\">🌐</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-title\">Multi-Language Support</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp4-body\">Site engineers, supervisors, and workers use SiteFlow in their preferred language — improving adoption and daily usage across diverse ground teams.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-card ocsp4-anim ocsp4-d4\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-bar\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp4-icon\">📱</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-title\">Mobile-First Design</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp4-body\">Designed for field teams working on the ground. Simple enough that site engineers pick it up on day one. Powerful enough for management dashboards and P&amp;L.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-card ocsp4-anim ocsp4-d5\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-bar\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp4-icon\">🔒</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-title\">Enterprise-Grade Security</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp4-body\">Cloud-hosted with controlled role-based access, regular backups, and encrypted data. Your project financials and site data are always secure and accessible to authorized users only.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-card ocsp4-anim ocsp4-d6\">\n<div class=\"ocsp4-bar\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp4-icon\">📊</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp4-title\">50+ Ready Reports</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp4-body\">Auto-synced dashboards covering materials, labour, progress, budgets, billing, and P&amp;L. Export as PDF or Excel for clients and management in one click.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ocsp5-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocsp5-wrap\">\n<div class=\"ocsp5-head ocsp5-anim\">\n<div class=\"ocsp5-eyebrow\"><span class=\"ocsp5-ey-dot\"></span>Customer Stories</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp5-h2\">Trusted by <em class=\"ocsp5-h2-em\">500+ construction teams.</em></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp5-grid\">\n<div class=\"ocsp5-card ocsp5-anim ocsp5-d1\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\">\n<div itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/SoftwareApplication\"></div>\n<div itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp5-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n<p class=\"ocsp5-quote\" itemprop=\"reviewBody\">“With SiteFlow, all the progress and cost details are visible in one place. It’s made client discussions much smoother because we’re now talking with actual site data instead of guesses.”</p>\n<div class=\"ocsp5-author\">\n<div class=\"ocsp5-avatar\">MK</div>\n<div itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n<span class=\"ocsp5-name\" itemprop=\"name\">Mr. Manish Kumar</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp5-company\">Reidius Infra, Jaipur  ·  Design &amp; Build</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp5-card ocsp5-anim ocsp5-d2\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\">\n<div itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/SoftwareApplication\"></div>\n<div itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp5-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n<p class=\"ocsp5-quote\" itemprop=\"reviewBody\">“SiteFlow helped us monitor spending at activity level instead of discovering overruns later. It brought financial visibility closer to daily execution — which is exactly what we needed.”</p>\n<div class=\"ocsp5-author\">\n<div class=\"ocsp5-avatar\">HP</div>\n<div itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n<span class=\"ocsp5-name\" itemprop=\"name\">Mr. Hiren Patel</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp5-company\">DCC, Mumbai  ·  Civil Construction</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp5-card ocsp5-anim ocsp5-d3\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Review\">\n<div itemprop=\"itemReviewed\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/SoftwareApplication\"></div>\n<div itemprop=\"reviewRating\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Rating\"></div>\n<span class=\"ocsp5-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n<p class=\"ocsp5-quote\" itemprop=\"reviewBody\">“We generate and share structured PDF reports directly from project data. It works reliably as a construction reporting software without confusion between site and office numbers.”</p>\n<div class=\"ocsp5-author\">\n<div class=\"ocsp5-avatar\">MT</div>\n<div itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n<span class=\"ocsp5-name\" itemprop=\"name\">Executive Founder</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp5-company\">Hydro Flow Qatar, Qatar  ·  Interior &amp; Building</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ocsp6-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocsp6-wrap\">\n<div class=\"ocsp6-head ocsp6-anim\">\n<div class=\"ocsp6-eyebrow\"><span class=\"ocsp6-ey-dot\"></span>FAQ</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-h2\">Questions about <em class=\"ocsp6-h2-em\">pricing?</em></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-list\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\">\n<div class=\"ocsp6-item ocsp6-anim ocsp6-d1\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocsp6-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Who can purchase SiteFlow?</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ocsp6-icon\">+</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><span itemprop=\"text\">SiteFlow is designed for a wide range of construction professionals — contractors, builders, architects, interior designers, EPC firms, and developers. Anyone in the construction industry looking to streamline project execution, cost control, and site management can benefit from SiteFlow.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-item ocsp6-anim ocsp6-d2\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocsp6-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Are plans customizable?</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ocsp6-icon\">+</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><span itemprop=\"text\">Yes. Every construction business has unique needs. If our existing plans don’t fully fit your requirements, reach out to our team and we can discuss a tailored plan that suits your team size and project complexity.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-item ocsp6-anim ocsp6-d3\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocsp6-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span itemprop=\"name\">What is the minimum billing?</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ocsp6-icon\">+</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><span itemprop=\"text\">The Business plan is billed at a minimum of ₹36,000/Year (3 users). The Business+ plan is billed at a minimum of ₹45,000/Year (3 users). Enterprise pricing is custom and depends on team size and requirements.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-item ocsp6-anim ocsp6-d4\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocsp6-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Do you offer discounts for annual subscriptions?</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ocsp6-icon\">+</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><span itemprop=\"text\">Yes, our pricing is already structured as annual plans with significant savings versus paying monthly. You save approximately 23% by committing annually. Contact our sales team for more details on available offers.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-item ocsp6-anim ocsp6-d5\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocsp6-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Who do I contact for pricing enquiries?</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ocsp6-icon\">+</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><span itemprop=\"text\">Our sales team is always available. You can book a free demo at siteflow.com/contact/ and a product specialist will walk you through all plans, custom pricing, and answer any questions about features or onboarding.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-item ocsp6-anim ocsp6-d6\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocsp6-q\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Is there a free trial available?</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ocsp6-icon\">+</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp6-a\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><span itemprop=\"text\">We offer a free guided product demo where our team shows you the software live, customised to your type of construction business. Book your free demo and see how SiteFlow works before making any commitment.</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"ocsp7-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocsp7-inner\">\n<div class=\"ocsp7-eyebrow ocsp7-anim\">\n<span class=\"ocsp7-ey-dot\"></span>Start Today\n    </div>\n<h2 class=\"ocsp7-h2 ocsp7-anim\">\n      Stop managing sites<br/>on <em class=\"ocsp7-h2-em\">WhatsApp.</em>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"ocsp7-sub ocsp7-anim\">\n      Join 500+ construction teams using SiteFlow to get real-time cost visibility, zero double entry, and complete site control — from BOQ to billing.\n    </p>\n<div class=\"ocsp7-btns ocsp7-anim ocsp7-d1\">\n<a class=\"ocsp7-btn ocsp7-btn-primary\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">Book a Free Demo</a>\n<a class=\"ocsp7-btn ocsp7-btn-outline\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/products/\">View All Features</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"
